                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing synthesis gas through oxidation of non-catalytic part of COREX melting gasification furnace",
                    "一种COREX熔融气化炉非催化部分氧化制备合成气的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for preparing synthesis gas through oxidation of a non-catalytic part of a COREX melting gasifier, and relates to the technical field of synthesis gas preparation. The method comprises the following steps: taking a vault area of the COREX melting gasification furnace as a reaction area, taking oxygen and natural gas as raw material gases, spraying the raw material gases into the vault area from a burner at the vault of the COREX melting gasification furnace, and carrying out a non-catalytic partial oxidation reaction of methane to prepare the synthesis gas taking hydrogen and carbon monoxide as main components. According to the technical scheme, in the prior art, the non-catalytic partial oxidation of the natural gas is accompanied by the reforming reaction of the natural gas, water vapor and carbon dioxide; by combining the high-temperature and high-pressure environment and high-speed airflow of the vault area, good dynamic conditions are provided for the oxidation reaction of the non-catalytic part of the natural gas, operation is easy, cost is low, efficiency is high, and industrial large-scale production and application and popularization are facilitated."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种COREX熔融气化炉非催化部分氧化制备合成气的方法，涉及合成气制备的技术领域。所述方法是以COREX熔融气化炉的拱顶区域为反应区，以氧气和天然气为原料气，由COREX熔融气化炉拱顶的烧嘴喷入拱顶区域，进行甲烷的非催化部分氧化反应，制备得到以氢气、一氧化碳为主要组分的合成气。本发明采用的是现有技术所不存在的天然气非催化部分氧化伴有天然气和水蒸气以及二氧化碳的重整反应技术方案，通过对氧气/天然气烧嘴以及循环粉尘喷吹烧嘴的结构设置和对原料气成分的控制，结合拱顶区域的高温高压环境和高速气流，为天然气非催化部分氧化反应提供了良好的动力学条件，操作简单、成本低、效率高，利于工业大规模生产和推广使用。"
                }
            ]
